videos.description: Michael Porter Jr. picks up the offensive rebound and puts it in to tally his first career points.
videos.headline: Porter gets first career points

videos.description: Jordan Barnett goes baseline and finishes with emphasis for the Tigers.
videos.headline: Missouri's Barnett destroys the rim

videos.description: Michael Porter Jr. checks out of the game only playing two minutes, holding his knee on the bench.
videos.headline: Porter sits on the bench holding his knee

videos.description: Missouri's Kevin Puryear knocks down a three at the top of the key to extend the Missouri lead.
videos.headline: Puryear's three extends Missouri lead

videos.description: Michael Porter Jr. scores just two points before exiting with a hip injury. Coach Cuonzo Martin explains the severity of the injury.
videos.headline: Porter's debut cut short by injury
